WEBVTT

00:01.937 --> 00:03.703
MIKE: <i>Joyce! Vince!</i>

00:03.706 --> 00:04.873
Let's move it!

00:04.874 --> 00:06.308
Your car's
all warmed up for you!

00:06.309 --> 00:08.610
So they can get
the hell out of here.

00:08.611 --> 00:10.145
Did you fill up their tank?

00:10.146 --> 00:11.813
Gas, air, wiper fluid.

00:11.814 --> 00:13.347
I set the GPS for the casino.

00:13.349 --> 00:14.883
I was gonna get their brakes
checked, but I figured,

00:14.884 --> 00:17.619
eh, what's meant to be's
meant to be.

00:17.620 --> 00:20.154
Hey! There's
the happy travelers!

00:20.156 --> 00:21.488
Got coffee for the driver.

00:21.490 --> 00:24.759
And wine for the passenger.

00:24.760 --> 00:27.027
It's before noon,
so I went with a crisp Chablis.

00:27.029 --> 00:28.296
Here we go.

00:28.297 --> 00:29.798
I don't know if I
should drink coffee.

00:29.799 --> 00:31.633
My stomach is rumbling
around like a dryer

00:31.634 --> 00:33.334
with one tennis shoe in it.

00:34.269 --> 00:36.638
I told you not to eat
that gas station sushi!

00:36.639 --> 00:38.540
But I figured I'd be safe.

00:38.541 --> 00:41.242
The guy who owns it is Japanese.

00:41.243 --> 00:42.811
He's Pakistani.

00:42.812 --> 00:46.613
Well, something is
about to say sayonara!

00:47.782 --> 00:51.486
Ah, he's been sitting
on that pot all morning.

00:51.487 --> 00:53.387
I don't know, maybe
a five-hour road trip

00:53.389 --> 00:55.056
isn't the best idea.

00:55.057 --> 00:58.125
I don't want him
to let loose in my Lexus.

00:58.127 --> 01:00.528
Well, maybe a road trip

01:00.529 --> 01:02.463
is just what the doctor ordered.

01:02.464 --> 01:04.831
Nothing binds me up
like traveling.

01:04.833 --> 01:06.234
It's true.

01:06.235 --> 01:09.203
Yeah, he only went once
on our whole honeymoon.

01:09.204 --> 01:10.471
That was two weeks!

01:10.472 --> 01:12.940
Why can't you do that here?

01:12.941 --> 01:15.743
Come on, you guys have been
dying to go play

01:15.744 --> 01:17.178
in that Texas Hold'em
tournament.

01:17.179 --> 01:19.479
You've been practicing
your poker face all month.

01:19.481 --> 01:21.882
Not poker face. Botox.

01:21.884 --> 01:24.652
Maybe I'll just go by myself,
and leave Vince at home.

01:24.653 --> 01:27.921
No! No! No! No! This is
his special trip, too.

01:27.923 --> 01:29.624
You know, in fact, I don't
think he's upstairs

01:29.625 --> 01:31.559
because of Pakistani sushi.

01:31.560 --> 01:32.793
I think he's just
so excited that he's

01:32.794 --> 01:35.662
lost control of his
bodily functions.

01:36.831 --> 01:39.367
You just want to send me off
with that ticking time bomb

01:39.368 --> 01:40.935
so you can have
the house to yourselves.

01:40.936 --> 01:42.001
Yes.

01:42.003 --> 01:44.671
I love you. Get out!

01:44.673 --> 01:46.440
Yeah, why do you think
we got Victoria that hotel room

01:46.441 --> 01:48.475
for her morticians' convention?

01:48.477 --> 01:49.610
It's not even three miles away.

01:49.611 --> 01:51.945
They got better parking here.

01:51.947 --> 01:53.746
Joyce, walk with me.

01:53.748 --> 01:56.750
You know that
gazebo-trellis thingy

01:56.751 --> 01:58.352
you've been wanting me to put
together in the backyard?

01:58.353 --> 01:59.486
Well, while you are gone,

01:59.488 --> 02:02.856
I will hire a guy
that will actually do it.

02:02.858 --> 02:05.559
He'll put the twinkle lights
in it, too?

02:05.560 --> 02:06.694
Well, of course.

02:06.695 --> 02:09.863
How else are you gonna
drink outside at night?

02:09.864 --> 02:13.167
I do like to drink
outside at night.

02:13.168 --> 02:14.335
Vince!

02:14.336 --> 02:15.903
Come on, we got to go!
Car's running!

02:15.904 --> 02:20.106
I took a Kaopectate and lined
my boxers with maxi pads.

02:21.775 --> 02:23.744
Hopefully that'll
hold me to Calumet City.

02:23.745 --> 02:24.811
Okay, there you go.

02:24.813 --> 02:25.913
And off you go.

02:25.914 --> 02:27.047
Bye! Drive safe! Hey!

02:27.048 --> 02:30.583
If you get hungry,
remember bananas bind!

02:33.554 --> 02:34.988
Oh, my God, they're gone.

02:34.989 --> 02:37.557
I can't believe we have
the whole house to ourselves.

02:37.559 --> 02:38.992
Yup. Home alone.
Good-bye pants.

02:38.993 --> 02:42.261
See you in 72 hours.

02:42.263 --> 02:43.563
That is such a good idea.

02:43.564 --> 02:47.400
Why am I still in this bra?

02:48.035 --> 02:50.837
