02:50.838 --> 02:53.774
♪ La, la-ba-dee-da ♪

02:53.775 --> 02:57.210
♪ For the first time
in my life ♪

02:57.211 --> 02:58.445
♪ I see love ♪

02:58.446 --> 03:00.881
